songs.lyrics:
[Hook]
Shawty, you know what it do
Wrists slit when I come through
I'm finna take 'em to the moon
I fly up like a balloon
All white linen, paint it true
Shawty, you know what it do
Smokin' double, give me two
Shawty, you know what it do

[Verse]
I don't give no fucks 'bout you
I take it all, can never lose
Only myself for my trues
Loving this shit since I was two
Got helicopters on my roof
I'm hiding far away from you
Sad Mob, we don't fuck with fools
I’m in the snow sipping Grey Goose
Double Gs on my shoe, Gs on my shoes

[Hook]
Shawty, you know what it do
Wrists slit when I come through
I'm finna take 'em to the moon
I fly up like a balloon
All white linen, paint it true
Shawty, you know what it do
songs.title: Shawty U Know What It Do
